OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be dry and warm with
OL,6,Flengthy sunny spells throughout the
OL,7,Fday, but sunshine turning somewhat
OL,8,Fhazier as cloud spreads south in the
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry at first with some hazy
OL,12,Fevening sunshine. It will stay mostly
OL,13,Fdry overnight, but turning cloudy over
OL,14,Fnorthern Argyll and the Isles with the
OL,15,Fodd spot of rain possible.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FIt will be dry throughout the
OL,18,Fday with variable cloud and some warm
OL,19,Fsunny spells. Generally cloudier over
OL,20,Fnorthern Argyll and the Isles.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
