OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,6,Fagain Tuesday with variable cloud and
OL,7,Fsome warm sunny spells. Mostly dry on
OL,8,FWednesday and Thursday but often
OL,9,Fcloudy with the chance of some patchy
OL,10,Flight rain. Breezy Thursday.
